  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalação de libpsl</title>

    <para>
      Instale <application>libpsl</application> executando os seguintes comandos:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>sed -i 's/env python/&amp;3/' src/psl-make-dafsa              &amp;&amp;
./configure --prefix=/usr --disable-static PYTHON=python3 &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      To test the results, issue: <command>make check</command>.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usuário(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>
  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="commands">
    <title>Explicações do Comando</title>

    <para>
      <command>sed -i ...</command>: This command forces the use of
<application>Python 3</application> in an utility.
